description: Try our easy to follow Thai Green Chicken Skewers recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Skewer & kebab,Gluten free,Tree nut free,Egg free,Low sugar,Sesame free,High protein,Soy free,Wheat free,Chicken,Dairy free,Peanut free
name: Thai Green Chicken Skewers Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Soak 12 bamboo skewers in water for 30 minutes.
Combine curry paste, coconut cream, chopped coriander stems (reserving leaves) and fish sauce in a bowl. Add chicken and coat well. Thread each chicken strip onto a skewer.
Heat a large grill pan over medium heat. Cook skewers for 6 minutes, turning, or until golden brown and cooked through.
Scatter over reserved coriander leaves and serve with lime wedges.
